videos.description: Texas Tech's David Moretti takes a hit but still sinks an off-balance jumper, drawing a foul.
videos.headline: Moretti hits off-balance jumper and draws foul

videos.description: Jalen Harris nails a deep 3-pointer at the buzzer, giving Arkansas a 33-30 lead over Texas Tech at halftime.
videos.headline: Harris hits deep 3 at halftime buzzer

videos.description: Adrio Bailey steals the ball and Daniel Gafford smashes a dunk for Arkansas.
videos.headline: Bailey steal sets up Gafford slam

videos.description: Jarrett Culver gives the Red Raiders a 10-point lead over the Razorbacks with a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Culver's 3 gives Texas Tech largest lead of game
